      "text": "windows and linux backup\nfor low network and min change systems\n     + less  insertions in data\n\nhow\n    backup job starts\n    server sends rpc to client\n    data chunked at client at fixed len\n    in first pass from client to server\n        we send only the chunk hash and md\n    server compares with old chunks ???\n    sends req in batches (???) to client \n    when a batch arrives at client client does below\n        1. sends data and md of those chunks\n        2. server compares , validates, sends ack\n    ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "windows and linux backup\nfor low network and min change systems\n     + less  insertions in data\n\nhow\n    backup job starts\n    server sends rpc to client\n    data chunked at client at fixed len\n    in first pass from client to server\n        we send only the chunk hash and md\n    server compares with old chunks ???\n    sends req in batches (???) to client \n    when a batch arrives at client client does below\n        1. sends data and md of those chunks\n        2. server compares , validates, sends ack\n    ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "AqNBIEBNGT6--cM9iGe8X",
