      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "chunk server?\n1. diff chunk server (chunk hash, system ip, id, ts, datastore url) \n    partitioned by source id\n2. available,fast w, slow r, raft to leader elect,replication\n\nbatching of req:\nmagneto does it\nget all mismatch chunks\ncreates batches + puts in table\npicks from table + set status to in progress + sends to client (thread a)\nclientsresponse picked + \n    { start transaction\n    dump data to s3\n    update progress\n    set chunk status to done/else\n    pick next batch and send to client\n    } end transaction]    (thread b)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "chunk server?\n1. diff chunk server (chunk hash, system ip, id, ts, datastore url) \n    partitioned by source id\n2. available,fast w, slow r, raft to leader elect,replication\n\nbatching of req:\nmagneto does it\nget all mismatch chunks\ncreates batches + puts in table\npicks from table + set status to in progress + sends to client (thread a)\nclientsresponse picked + \n    { start transaction\n    dump data to s3\n    update progress\n    set chunk status to done/else\n    pick next batch and send to client\n    } end transaction]    (thread b)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
